creator: ATRANGII NETWORK PRIVATE LIMITED
descriptionHtml:
ATRANGII-Dekhte Raho is your one stop destination to watch the best of Hindi Television content.

ATRANGII APP will showcase rich original programming line-up. The channel is set to telecast limited series with the help of international production tie-ups. It will bring finite series with worldwide elegance production, giving content material a definitive element over presently produced indicates inside the Hindi GEC area. Currently, the channel is catering to HSM audiences with fiction and non-fiction collection with varied genres like mythology, comedy, drama, horror, suspense, thriller & many more.

ATRANGII APP Features :-
-Download videos to watch offline
-Cast your phone or tablet to the big screen with Chromecast
The app is available to download for free.

NEW CONCEPT ON TV:-
With an innovative concept and its ability to tap into new audiences, The company plans to launch OTT on TV. It shall provide the same experience at a fraction of the cost and with higher quality!

This disruptive strategy is unique because it combines technology, media and telecom to create a new market.

OTT content on TV is a part of the daily life of millions – OTT on TV.

The OTT segment holds a strong share in the Indian market. It is now reaching new heights and leading the way towards mass adoption and distribution of entertainment content with 95.6% distribution in India on networks such as TATA PLAY, DISH TV, AIRTEL DIGITAL TV, HATHWAY, DEN, FASTWAY and many other micro and mini micro networks.

title: Atrangii

creator: ATRANGII NETWORK PRIVATE LIMITED
descriptionHtml:
Catch all your favourite ATRANGII TV shows on the OTT app at your convenience. Whatever is your favourite genre, we have an exciting content bouquet ready to entertain you. Our new and exclusive Television shows include comedy, crime, drama, mythology, romance, thriller and much more.

You can binge watch episodes of our best shows like Parshuram and Hara Sindoor. Every time you log in, you will discover a new Rang (colour) of entertainment with in our unique Atrangii tinge.

By subscribing to our premium offering, you can not only watch your favourite shows and sports ad-free but also enjoy exclusive content available only as part of the subscription model.

Benefits of subscription
● New releases every week
● Access to premium shows
● Ad free entertainment
● Full movies/shows
● Streaming and downloading to watch offline in full 1080p HD
● Chromecast enables you to cast your smartphone or tablet to a bigger screen

The premium subscription service costs very less and does not affect much to your pocket.

We know your choice and we understand that an Indian entertainment bouquet is incomplete without a dash of Cricket. You can watch select international T20 matches and highlights on the App. We will keep garnishing the platter with newer spices. Standby for a variety of sports action from all over India and across the world in coming days. Dekhte Raho….

You can binge watch episodes of our best shows like Parshuram and Hara Sindoor. Every time you log in, you will discover a new Rang (colour) of entertainment with in our unique Atrangii tinge.

By subscribing to our premium offering, you can not only watch your favourite shows and sports ad-free but also enjoy exclusive content available only as part of the subscription model.

Benefits of subscription
● New releases every week
● Access to premium shows
● Ad free entertainment
● Full movies/shows
● Streaming and downloading to watch offline in full 1080p HD
● Chromecast enables you to cast your smartphone or tablet to a bigger screen

The premium subscription service costs very less and does not affect much to your pocket.

We know your choice and we understand that an Indian entertainment bouquet is incomplete without a dash of Cricket. You can watch select international T20 matches and highlights on the App. We will keep garnishing the platter with newer spices. Standby for a variety of sports action from all over India and across the world in coming days. Dekhte Raho…

descriptionHtml:
🌟 Welcome to Atrangii – Your Ultimate Entertainment Hub! 🌟
Dive into a world where every genre and preference finds its perfect match. Atrangii is your gateway to an extraordinary array of content that spans drama, romance, action, thrillers, horror, and more! Whether you're craving the latest international hits or beloved regional favorites, Atrangii has it all.
Top Features:
🎬 Exclusive Content: Immerse yourself in a rich library of trending shows like Ansuni, Rosy Maam, Tadap, Mastram, Graduate, Haveli, and The Devil Inside. Our exclusive collection ensures you’re always at the forefront of fresh, engaging entertainment.
🌏 International Shows: Experience the best of global entertainment with top-rated Korean dramas, captivating Russian series, intriguing Pakistani dramas, thrilling Turkish shows, and exciting Chinese series – all dubbed in Hindi for a seamless viewing experience.
🎭 Regional Entertainment: Enjoy a diverse selection of shows and movies in various regional languages. With Atrangii, you’ll feel right at home with content that resonates with your cultural preferences.
✨ User-Friendly Interface: Navigate effortlessly with our intuitive interface. Discover new favorites through organized categories and personalized recommendations designed to make your viewing experience as enjoyable as possible.
🎥 High-Quality Streaming: Relish the ultimate viewing experience with our high-definition streaming. Enjoy crisp, clear visuals and immerse yourself in the content with our advanced streaming technology.
🆕 Regular Updates: Stay on top of the latest entertainment with frequent updates to our content library. Be the first to explore new shows and movies as we continually refresh our offerings.
With Atrangii, you don’t just watch; you experience the best in entertainment from around the globe. From exclusive shows to international sensations and regional gems, Atrangii is your one-stop destination for all things entertainment.
Why settle for ordinary when you can have Atrangii? Join us today and explore endless possibilities with premium content right at your fingertips.📱
